OL,5,BChunky Fringe 2021.          W +//'    
OL,7,EChunky FringeBatEDigitiser LiveB2021   
OL,8,Bmarks the tentative return of in-person
OL,9,Bteletext events.                       
OL,11,BThe event is organised byEDavid Walford
OL,12,Band occupies the Hatch End Suite at    
OL,13,EHarrow Arts CentreBfrom 11-5 on the 4th
OL,14,Bof September. See p107                 
OL,17,BDon't forget you canEadd your own pages
OL,18,Eto chunkytext!BSee user guide on p103. 
