OL,5,BTeletext Pages from VHS.               
OL,7,BSome of the pages on Chunkytext were   
OL,8,Brecovered fromEold VHS recordingsBand  
OL,9,Bpainstakingly restored by members of   
OL,10,Bthe Teletext Restoration Team.         
OL,12,BAs such some will contain references to
OL,13,Bpages which are not present on this    
OL,14,Bsystem. TheEFastextBlinks have been    
OL,15,Baltered to remove the missing pages.   
OL,17,BIt should go without saying not to use 
OL,18,Bthe defunct address or phone numbers!  
